__________________________________________________________________

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_GDFFileReader_Outputs|
 * |OVP_DocEnd_BoxAlgorithm_GDFFileReader_Outputs|

 * |OVP_DocBegin_BoxAlgorithm_GDFFileReader_Output1|
